Why didn't she go to any of the other villages?

363
00:22:48,450 --> 00:22:50,620
当你问起科尔弗  韦德为什么去找他时
When you asked Colfur why Wade was there,

364
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:53,650
他和凯特琳对视了一眼
there was this look between Colfur and Katelyn.

365
00:22:53,720 --> 00:22:56,590
似乎他不想让她说话
It was like he wanted to be sure she wouldn't speak.

366
00:23:01,500 --> 00:23:02,940
摩根
Morgan!

367
00:23:02,940 --> 00:23:03,900
天啊
Oh, my Lord!

368
00:23:03,970 --> 00:23:05,970
西比尔
Sibyl.

369
00:23:07,800 --> 00:23:09,920
我们在林子里找到她
She was found in the woods.

370
00:23:09,920 --> 00:23:10,970
大家让开
Get away from her.

371
00:23:19,680 --> 00:23:21,820
把她抬到她床上
Let's get her to her bed.

372
00:23:21,890 --> 00:23:24,550
不  去我房间
No, my chamber.

373
00:23:33,090 --> 00:23:35,060
连修女都被打了
The holy mother beaten

374
00:23:35,130 --> 00:23:37,170
我们都不安全
none of us are safe.

375
00:23:48,910 --> 00:23:51,950
快  去拿水和布
Run, fetch water and cloths!

376
00:24:01,760 --> 00:24:04,230
他们看到了...
They see...

377
00:24:04,300 --> 00:24:08,200
...你在和他们一起经受痛苦
...that you suffer with them.

378
00:24:08,270 --> 00:24:13,600
还说我不懂政治吗
Now tell me I know nothing about politics.

379
00:24:15,540 --> 00:24:18,910
别浪费时间  孩子
Don't waste the moment, child.

380
00:24:18,980 --> 00:24:21,450
好好利用这机会
Use it.

381
00:24:21,510 --> 00:24:23,610
去吧
Go.

382
00:24:25,520 --> 00:24:27,590
去啊
Go.

383
00:24:37,000 --> 00:24:39,060
我需要帮助
I need help.

384
00:24:39,130 --> 00:24:41,130
你需要女人出马
You want a woman's touch?

385
00:24:41,200 --> 00:24:44,470
是
Mm.

386
00:24:44,540 --> 00:24:47,070
她不是求助而是逃生
She ran instead of getting help.

387
00:24:47,070 --> 00:24:48,970
这没道理
It doesn't make sense.

388
00:24:49,040 --> 00:24:51,540
我必须确定
I have to be sure.

389
00:24:51,610 --> 00:24:54,510
我必须确定他是有罪  才能判他死刑
I can't sentence a man to death unless I'm sure.

390
00:24:54,580 --> 00:24:56,680
他杀了另一个男人
He killed another man.

391
00:24:56,750 --> 00:24:59,680
为何审判他会如此困扰你
Why does sentencing him bother you so much?

392
00:24:59,750 --> 00:25:01,320
因为我想让我们的判决
Because I want our justice

393
00:25:01,320 --> 00:25:03,050
比以前更严明  更公正
to be better than what's gone before.

394
00:25:03,120 --> 00:25:05,540
因为我想  有时候
And because I think that sometimes maybe

395
00:25:05,540 --> 00:25:07,690
人也许会为正当理由而犯错
people do the wrong thing for the right reasons.

396
00:25:15,800 --> 00:25:17,840
这儿很美
It is beautiful.

397
00:25:17,900 --> 00:25:21,540
我有时会来这里思考
I sometimes come here to think.

398
00:25:21,610 --> 00:25:24,840
我以前从没见过大海
I've never seen the sea before.

399
00:25:28,810 --> 00:25:31,120
亚瑟是个好人
Arthur's a good man.

400
00:25:31,180 --> 00:25:33,580
他愿意倾听人们的疾苦
He listens to the people.

401
00:25:33,650 --> 00:25:35,420
他真的关心大家
He really cares.

402
00:25:35,490 --> 00:25:38,820
他帮不了我  没人帮得了
He can't help me. No one can.

403
00:25:38,890 --> 00:25:41,730
这是我的错
It's my fault.

404
00:25:41,790 --> 00:25:43,700
为什么
Why?

405
00:25:43,700 --> 00:25:45,230
我逃跑了
I ran.

406
00:25:45,300 --> 00:25:47,230
我父亲叫我快跑
My father told me to.

407
00:25:47,300 --> 00:25:50,100
我们知道韦德快来了
We knew Wade was coming.

408
00:25:50,170 --> 00:25:53,070
他来干嘛
What was he coming for?

409
00:25:55,940 --> 00:25:59,880
我们的头领会享有每个女孩的贞操
The head man takes every girl as she becomes a woman.

410
00:25:59,940 --> 00:26:01,610
不可能
No!

411
00:26:01,610 --> 00:26:03,280
就是这回事
It's the way.

412
00:26:03,350 --> 00:26:05,620
难道没人阻止吗
Do people not try and stop this?

413
00:26:05,680 --> 00:26:09,090
我们斗不过韦德和尤恩的家族
You don't stand against Wade and Ewan's kin.

414
00:26:21,400 --> 00:26:23,470
伊格兰说得对
Igraine was right.

415
00:26:27,370 --> 00:26:28,530
是  这就是原因
Yes, this is why.

416
00:26:28,530 --> 00:26:29,970
被她发现了
Heh... She finds out,

417
00:26:29,980 --> 00:26:32,020
现在来打扰的人没完没了
and now it's an endless stream of visitors

418
00:26:32,020 --> 00:26:33,680
还偏偏是在我想要思考的时候
just when I'm trying to think.

419
00:26:35,580 --> 00:26:37,840
还有谁来过
Who else has been here?

420
00:26:37,840 --> 00:26:39,720
那不是重点
Hmm? That's not the point.

421
00:26:39,780 --> 00:26:43,020
你是说只有我吗
Huh... You mean just me?

422
00:26:43,090 --> 00:26:47,720
是我在没完没了的打扰你
An endless stream of me? Hm!

423
00:26:49,660 --> 00:26:51,630
你想要什么
What is it you want?

424
00:26:51,630 --> 00:26:53,160
你就这样独自待这里
You were here all alone.

425
00:26:53,230 --> 00:26:55,130
我需要时间
I needed some time.

426
00:26:55,200 --> 00:26:57,500
这是什么
What is this?

427
00:26:57,570 --> 00:27:00,340
我想把一切都列出来
I wanted to lay it all out.

428
00:27:02,970 --> 00:27:05,040
这些都是什么意思
What does it all mean?

429
00:27:05,110 --> 00:27:08,180
那代表了第一波...
Oh, that just shows the first wave is...

430
00:27:08,240 --> 00:27:10,150
...业已完成
...ostensibly complete.

431
00:27:10,210 --> 00:27:11,930
但我们已经落后了
But we've fallen behind.

432
00:27:11,930 --> 00:27:13,480
还有很多事情需要做
There's so much more to do.

433
00:27:13,550 --> 00:27:15,180
比如建个图书馆
The library.

434
00:27:18,620 --> 00:27:21,390
第一波  是什么意思
What do you mean, "First wave"?

435
00:27:21,460 --> 00:27:23,350
就是带你来这里
Well, getting you here--

436
00:27:23,360 --> 00:27:25,960
占领卡米洛特  招募人才
occupying Camelot, recruiting people.

437
00:27:26,030 --> 00:27:28,150
你的审讯怎么样
How's your trial?

438
00:27:28,150 --> 00:27:29,270
你来吗
Will you come?

439
00:27:29,270 --> 00:27:31,050
不去
No.

440
00:27:31,050 --> 00:27:31,970
为什么
Why?

441
00:27:31,970 --> 00:27:33,410
因为你已有了计划
You had the big idea.

442
00:27:33,470 --> 00:27:35,580
好好干吧
See it through.

443
00:27:35,580 --> 00:27:36,440
我会的
I will.

444
00:27:36,440 --> 00:27:38,040
很好
Good.

445
00:27:41,310 --> 00:27:44,250
我很快就会好起来
I'll be fine soon.

446
00:27:44,320 --> 00:27:46,390
我只需要...
I just needed...

447
00:27:49,660 --> 00:27:51,690
...就像现在这样
...this.

448
00:27:55,660 --> 00:27:57,230
我会关注你的
I'll be watching.

449
00:28:13,520 --> 00:28:15,130
又被伏击
Yet another ambush.

450
00:28:15,130 --> 00:28:16,050
这是个严重的问题...
This is a serious trouble...

451
00:28:16,050 --> 00:28:17,810
...出门没有安全保障
...travel about without protection.

452
00:28:17,810 --> 00:28:18,990
告诉女人们...
Tell the women...

453
00:28:19,050 --> 00:28:21,150
摩根小姐
Lady Morgan.

454
00:28:27,330 --> 00:28:28,300
我必须道歉
I must apologize.

455
00:28:28,300 --> 00:28:29,760
不  不
No, no, no. No, no, no.

456
00:28:29,830 --> 00:28:31,820
不必这样  她怎么样了
Not at all. How is she?

457
00:28:31,820 --> 00:28:33,360
有人照料着她
She's being attended.

458
00:28:35,800 --> 00:28:37,320
你们得原谅我
You'll have to forgive me.

459
00:28:37,330 --> 00:28:38,650
她就像我的母亲
She's been a mother to me

460
00:28:38,650 --> 00:28:40,370
从我小时候就开始照顾我
since I was a little girl.

461
00:28:40,440 --> 00:28:42,960
怎么会这样
How can this happen?

462
00:28:42,960 --> 00:28:44,040
请
Please.

463
00:28:44,110 --> 00:28:45,380
喝吧
Drink.

464
00:28:45,380 --> 00:28:46,650
谢谢
Thank you.

465
00:28:50,490 --> 00:28:54,020
她的马有彭德拉根的标记
Her horse was carrying the Pendragon symbol.

466
00:28:55,960 --> 00:28:58,190
她带了我们的印旗吗
She was wearing our colours?

467
00:28:58,260 --> 00:29:00,630
但这本该能保护我们啊
But... but this is our protection.

468
00:29:00,700 --> 00:29:03,630
我商旅途中一直执此印旗
I fly this banner along my trading routes.

469
00:29:03,700 --> 00:29:05,670
但还是被袭击
It's still attacked.

470
00:29:05,730 --> 00:29:07,530
这印旗飘遍我们的村庄
The banner is flown over my village,

471
00:29:07,600 --> 00:29:09,740
可我们的粮仓还是被抢
and yet our grain stores are robbed,

472
00:29:09,800 --> 00:29:12,100
我们的姑娘还是被掳走
our young women are taken.

473
00:29:12,170 --> 00:29:14,710
到处都没王法  无法无天
There's no control. None at all.

474
00:29:14,770 --> 00:29:17,280
我们都是忠诚的子民
We are all loyal subjects.

475
00:29:17,340 --> 00:29:19,910
这...这...
Well, this... this...

476
00:29:19,980 --> 00:29:21,920
...这可称不上保护
...this is not protection.

477
00:29:21,980 --> 00:29:24,380
我们理解  他是您弟弟
We understand he is your brother.

478
00:29:24,450 --> 00:29:28,090
但王土已然混乱
But the land moves further into chaos

479
00:29:28,160 --> 00:29:30,060
并日趋恶化
every day.

480
00:29:30,130 --> 00:29:32,160
这才是真相
And that is the real truth.

481
00:29:34,100 --> 00:29:37,370
我不会听之任之
I will not let this happen.

482
00:29:37,440 --> 00:29:40,300
我发誓
I will not!

483
00:29:40,370 --> 00:29:43,070
还有人也感觉不公吗
Are there others who feel betrayed?

484
00:29:43,140 --> 00:29:45,910
是的  有很多人
Yes, there are others.

485
00:29:45,980 --> 00:29:48,750
我要代表我们所有人
I will send a messenger

486
00:29:48,810 --> 00:29:51,580
送个信给我弟弟
to my brother to represent all of us.

487
00:29:51,650 --> 00:29:53,550
当他知道这些  他会有所表示
When he knows of this, he will act.

488
00:29:53,620 --> 00:29:56,960
我知道他会有所补偿  相信他
I know he will want to make redress. Have faith in him.

489
00:29:57,020 --> 00:29:58,960
同时
In the meantime,

490
00:29:59,030 --> 00:30:01,660
告诉其他有此遭遇之人
send word to others who feel this way.

491
00:30:01,730 --> 00:30:04,360
叫他们今晚来彭德拉根的城堡
Tell them to come to Castle Pendragon tonight.

492
00:30:04,430 --> 00:30:08,500
告诉他们国王会给大家一个答复
Tell them the king will come to his sister's call.

493
00:30:14,980 --> 00:30:17,410
我要派人去送信吗
Shall I send for the messenger?

494
00:30:17,480 --> 00:30:20,380
别麻烦了
Don't bother.

495
00:30:20,450 --> 00:30:22,380
我们在等什么
So what are we waiting for?

496
00:30:22,450 --> 00:30:25,000
他现在就该被处决了
He should be dead and buried by now.

497
00:30:25,000 --> 00:30:27,560
和你的人一起等着
Go wait with your people.

498
00:30:32,230 --> 00:30:33,250
这有何用
How does this help?

499
00:30:33,250 --> 00:30:35,470
我拿起石头  砸了他的头
I got a rock, I smashed it on his head.

500
00:30:35,470 --> 00:30:37,170
这是我自作自受
I deserve what I get.

501
00:30:37,170 --> 00:30:38,540
大家必须了解实情
The people have to know.

502
00:30:38,600 --> 00:30:40,250
我可以宽恕你  因为有正当理由
I can spare you; there was justification.

503
00:30:40,250 --> 00:30:41,540
但大家得知道为什么
But the people have to know why.

504
00:30:41,610 --> 00:30:42,920
不  我说过我不想那样
No. I've told you no.

505
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:44,970
如果你不说出来  这种事还会继续
If you don't speak about this, it will keep on happening.

506
00:30:45,040 --> 00:30:46,740
那与我无关
That's not my responsibility.

507
00:30:46,740 --> 00:30:48,810
那一切怎么会改变
Then how does anything ever change?!

508
00:30:48,880 --> 00:30:51,400
没那么简单
It's not that simple.

509
00:30:51,400 --> 00:30:53,080
为什么
Why?

510
00:30:56,550 --> 00:30:58,490
你出去一下  凯特琳
Go out, Katelyn.

511
00:30:58,560 --> 00:31:00,920
不
No.

512
00:31:00,990 --> 00:31:04,260
出去  拜托
I said go out. Please.

513
00:31:12,840 --> 00:31:14,770
韦德的家族...
Wade's family...

514
00:31:14,840 --> 00:31:17,910
...拥有村庄所有的土地
...owns all the land the village is on.

515
00:31:17,980 --> 00:31:20,940
每种庄稼的第一季收成都归他们
They get the first realm of every crop.

516
00:31:21,010 --> 00:31:23,440
秋季  他们会开垦
They plough the first furrow

517
00:31:23,440 --> 00:31:25,050
每个农场的第一条田沟
of every farm come autumn.

518
00:31:28,490 --> 00:31:30,920
我结婚的前一晚
The night before my wedding,

519
00:31:30,990 --> 00:31:34,320
韦德和尤恩的父亲来行使他的权利
Wade and Ewan's father claimed his tithe.

520
00:31:37,990 --> 00:31:42,600
我不是本地人  我没听说过...
I was an outsider. I... I hadn't heard...

521
00:31:42,670 --> 00:31:47,030
...头领可以享有每个女人的初夜
...head man was always the first for every woman.

522
00:31:47,100 --> 00:31:51,810
凯特琳的母亲...在我们婚后两天...
Katelyn's mother... told me...

523
00:31:51,870 --> 00:31:54,810
...告诉了我实情
...two days after we were married.

524
00:31:56,710 --> 00:32:00,380
她生凯特林琳的时候死于难产
She died giving birth to Katelyn.

525
00:32:00,450 --> 00:32:04,150
凯特琳  韦德和尤恩是...
Katelyn, Wade, and Ewan are...

526
00:32:04,220 --> 00:32:06,120
...血亲
...kin.

527
00:32:06,190 --> 00:32:08,160
韦德和尤恩并不在意
Wade and Ewan don't care.

528
00:32:08,220 --> 00:32:10,260
那些兄弟占有了每个姑娘
Those brothers come for every girl.

529
00:32:10,330 --> 00:32:12,250
你们为什么不离开呢
Then why didn't you leave?

530
00:32:12,250 --> 00:32:13,960
我什么都没做错
I did nothing wrong!

531
00:32:14,030 --> 00:32:15,870
你必须说出事实
You have to speak.

532
00:32:15,870 --> 00:32:17,300
得阻止这样的事
This has to stop!

533
00:32:17,370 --> 00:32:18,450
不行
I can't!

534
00:32:18,460 --> 00:32:21,900
凯特琳不知道她不是我亲生的
Katelyn doesn't know she's not mine.

535
00:32:21,970 --> 00:32:25,970
如果她知道了  我会永远失去她
If she knew, she... I'll have lost her!

536
00:32:26,040 --> 00:32:27,710
看看我
Oh, look at me,

537
00:32:27,780 --> 00:32:30,710
老大不小了  哭得像个小孩
a grown man, crying like a baby.

538
00:32:32,780 --> 00:32:35,220
连结你们的不是血脉
It's not blood that ties you together;

539
00:32:35,280 --> 00:32:37,690
而是你们共同的回忆
it's the memories you share.

540
00:32:39,590 --> 00:32:40,670
是你教授她的一切
Everything you taught her,

541
00:32:40,670 --> 00:32:42,960
是你为她放弃的一切
everything you gave up for her--

542
00:32:43,030 --> 00:32:44,990
那是你的爱
that's your love;

543
00:32:44,990 --> 00:32:47,230
那才是她所在意的
that's what flows through her.

544
00:32:47,300 --> 00:32:51,170
告诉她  你会看到她有多爱你
Tell her and you'll see how much she loves you.

545
00:32:54,470 --> 00:32:57,240
我知道的
I know.

546
00:32:57,310 --> 00:32:59,070
你以为村里的姑娘们
You think the girls in the village

547
00:32:59,140 --> 00:33:01,540
不会谈论这些吗
don't talk about this?

548
00:33:03,610 --> 00:33:06,920
我一直都知道
I've always known.

549
00:33:06,980 --> 00:33:09,190
但是...
And...

550
00:33:09,250 --> 00:33:12,160
...我从没有因此而不爱你
...I never loved you any the less.

551
00:33:12,220 --> 00:33:17,160
你...是我的父亲
You... are my father.

552
00:33:43,820 --> 00:33:46,490
韦德过来想占有她
Wade had come for her.

553
00:33:46,560 --> 00:33:50,060
我叫她逃跑
And I told her to run.

554
00:33:50,130 --> 00:33:52,260
我叫她忘记我
I told her to forget me

555
00:33:52,330 --> 00:33:55,270
远离我  有多远跑多远
and get away-- as far away as she could.

556
00:33:55,330 --> 00:33:56,760
我告诉他  别靠近我女儿
I told him I'd kill him

557
00:33:56,760 --> 00:33:59,370
不然就杀了他
before I'd let him near my girl.

558
00:34:01,340 --> 00:34:04,380
那就是争斗的原因
That's how the fight started.

559
00:34:09,480 --> 00:34:11,420
你有什么要说的吗
Have you anything to say?

560
00:34:11,480 --> 00:34:13,920
这些我们都知道
We knew all this.

561
00:34:13,990 --> 00:34:16,320
那是我们的生存之道
That's the way we live.

562
00:34:16,390 --> 00:34:18,020
你们村的习俗
The customs of your village

563
