Why does it bother you?

587
00:36:28,620 --> 00:36:31,190
因为有时我能隐约看到
Because sometimes I see glimpses

588
00:36:31,260 --> 00:36:34,330
你将成为什么样的人
of the man you might be.

589
00:36:43,500 --> 00:36:46,400
