...we have to stop it.

600
00:37:44,630 --> 00:37:46,730
一定
We will.

601
00:37:51,270 --> 00:37:53,200
谢谢
Thank you.

602
00:37:53,270 --> 00:37:57,070
谢谢你去引导凯特琳
For what you did with Katelyn.

603
