After the amount of injuries you've got,

609
00:38:23,480 --> 00:38:25,300
这剑最好能成为传奇
it had better become legendary.

610
00:38:25,370 --> 00:38:28,170
那是把好剑  但要成为传奇
Ah, it's a great sword, but it'll only be...

611
00:38:28,240 --> 00:38:31,870
