...legendary if he does something legendary with it.

612
00:38:34,480 --> 00:38:37,280
梅林
Merlin...

613
00:38:37,350 --> 00:38:39,980
你到底是什么人
Who are you?

614
00:38:42,050 --> 00:38:44,020
我该怎么回答
How am I supposed to answer that?

615
00:38:44,090 --> 00:38:48,520
