The same.

618
00:38:55,670 --> 00:38:58,630
-你生在何处  -很重要吗
- Where were you born? - Does it matter?

619
00:38:58,700 --> 00:39:01,870
不重要  但我好奇
It doesn't matter, but I'm interested.

620
00:39:03,810 --> 00:39:06,080
你总是有所隐瞒
You hide.

621
