What about you?

624
00:39:16,820 --> 00:39:18,890
你知道我的一切
You know everything about me.

625
00:39:18,960 --> 00:39:20,720
康沃尔
Cornwall.

626
00:39:20,790 --> 00:39:22,260
尤瑟
Uther.

627
00:39:22,330 --> 00:39:23,890
然后到了这儿
Here.

628
00:39:23,960 --> 00:39:26,060
但在康沃尔之前
But before Cornwall...

629
00:39:26,130 --> 00:39:29,070
你又是什么样的人
Who were you then?

630
00:39:34,670 --> 00:39:37,910
当时我很
I was...

631
00:39:37,980 --> 00:39:40,180
坚强
...strong.

632
00:39:40,240 --> 00:39:43,050
固执
Opinionated.

633
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:47,920
天真
Naive...

634
00:39:47,990 --> 00:39:50,690
而且充满希望
...and full of hope.

635
00:39:50,760 --> 00:39:53,790
生长在条件优渥之家
Living comfortably in a family with means.

636
00:39:53,860 --> 00:39:56,360
你当时的梦想是什么
What did you dream of?

637
00:39:58,800 --> 00:40:03,300
我梦想有一个能够平等待我的夫君
I dreamt of a husband who'd treat me as an equal.

638
00:40:03,370 --> 00:40:05,940
你找到他了吗
Did you ever find him?

639
00:40:08,870 --> 00:40:10,940
没有
No.

640
00:40:21,520 --> 00:40:24,050
很遗憾
I'm sorry for that.

641
00:40:26,460 --> 00:40:28,790
我也是
So am I.

642
00:40:38,740 --> 00:40:42,710
-不行  -怎么了
- No! - What's the matter?

643
00:40:42,770 --> 00:40:44,710
靠近我的人都会被焚烧致死
People who get close to me get burned.

644
00:40:44,780 --> 00:40:48,880
你怎么会成为这种人的
How did you become such a man?!

645
00:40:54,820 --> 00:40:57,890
-多上点酒  -是的  修女
- Be generous with the drink. - Yes, Holy Mother.

646
00:41:00,530 --> 00:41:03,590
确保每个人都能吃好
Make sure everyone is well fed.

647
00:41:05,530 --> 00:41:09,700
是你  你跟国王的姐姐同住
It's you. You live here with the king's sister?

648
00:41:09,770 --> 00:41:12,970
不  我只是为了食物而来
No, I don't. I came for the food.

649
00:41:13,040 --> 00:41:15,200
你在给侍女们下命令  你一定住在这里
You were giving orders to the servants. You live here.

650
00:41:15,270 --> 00:41:18,970
