Why does Morgan's nun pay me to beat the pulp out of her?

651
00:41:19,040 --> 00:41:24,410
我需要一个栖身之所
I... needed a roof over my head.

652
00:41:24,480 --> 00:41:27,280
这样能让他们心软
And this... persuaded them.

653
00:41:29,860 --> 00:41:32,690
求你了  别对我妄加评判
Please. Don't judge me.

654
00:42:07,690 --> 00:42:11,130
-东西都在这儿了吗  -是的  谢谢
- Is this everything? - Yes, sir. - Thank you.

655
00:42:11,200 --> 00:42:13,530
你得赶不少路
You've got a lot of ground to cover.

656
00:42:20,270 --> 00:42:23,010
最好别犯傻惹我出手
Don't make the mistake of taking me on.

657
00:42:23,080 --> 00:42:26,540
我们有我们自己的规矩
You see, we have our own justice.

658
00:42:26,610 --> 00:42:30,620
我也有我的  我母亲就曾被人强暴过
So do I. My mother knew what it was to be raped.

659
00:42:30,680 --> 00:42:34,390
所以你们这种人  在我心里有着特殊的位子
So I keep a special place in my heart for people like you.

660
00:42:34,450 --> 00:42:36,150
天高皇帝远  这里是我说了算
Your king doesn't rule around here; I do.

661
00:42:36,220 --> 00:42:38,190
适可而止吧  多说多错
You the more you talk, the more trouble you're in.

662
00:42:38,260 --> 00:42:41,890
我说科尔弗  你就是这种人么
So, Colfur, is this who you are?

663
00:42:41,960 --> 00:42:46,530
躲在个毛头小子和他的武士身后
Hiding behind a boy king and his warriors? Eh, Colfur!

664
00:42:46,600 --> 00:42:49,000
这个男人已经受到了处罚
This man has been banished!

665
00:42:49,070 --> 00:42:51,840
我正在执行判决
And I'm carrying out his sentence.

666
00:42:51,900 --> 00:42:54,600
请别妨碍我
Please don't get in my way.

667
00:43:05,820 --> 00:43:07,920
我们有麻烦了
We have a problem.

668
00:43:13,890 --> 00:43:16,360
-..杀了我哥哥  -我最后一次警告你
- ...killed my brother. - This is your last warning!

669
00:43:16,430 --> 00:43:18,560
滚回家去
Go back to your dwellings.

670
00:43:18,630 --> 00:43:21,260
怎么着  大个子
What the matter, big man?

671
00:43:21,330 --> 00:43:23,700
不敢跟我们打吗
Are you afraid to fight?

672
00:43:34,910 --> 00:43:37,550
你会得到应有的处罚
Ah, you'll get your rightful punishment.

673
00:43:37,620 --> 00:43:39,550
你女儿也将履行她的义务
And your girl will get her due.

674
00:43:45,690 --> 00:43:48,090
就是他
Him.

675
00:43:51,460 --> 00:43:53,530
区区小事
This is not a problem.

676
00:44:16,760 --> 00:44:20,230
各位
My people.

677
00:44:20,300 --> 00:44:24,060
欢迎今晚来到彭德拉根的城堡
I welcome you tonight to Castle Pendragon.

678
00:44:24,130 --> 00:44:26,630
国王呢  他来了吗
Where's the king? Has he come?

679
00:44:26,700 --> 00:44:29,400
很遗憾  他公务繁忙  无暇理会我
I'm sorry to say that he was too busy to talk to me.

680
00:44:29,470 --> 00:44:31,800
什么
What?

681
00:44:31,870 --> 00:44:33,610
他把我的信使打发回来了
He sent my messenger back

682
00:44:33,670 --> 00:44:36,980
说他太忙  无暇顾及我们的担忧
with word that he was too busy to address our concerns.

683
00:44:37,040 --> 00:44:41,480
-太  太忙  -我理解你们的心情
- Too... too busy? - I share your frustration.

684
00:44:41,550 --> 00:44:44,250
我也无法再粉饰太平了
I cannot pretend otherwise.

685
00:44:46,820 --> 00:44:48,990
我现在觉得
It seems to me now...

686
00:44:49,060 --> 00:44:53,590
我们正处于绝壁之上
...that we stand on the very brink.

687
00:44:53,660 --> 00:44:56,090
过去在我父亲的庇护下的一切安定
Everything that was once so secure

688
00:44:56,160 --> 00:45:00,130
现在都受到了威胁
under my father's reign is now under threat.

689
00:45:00,200 --> 00:45:04,470
我们全都身陷险境
All of us are in danger.

690
00:45:04,540 --> 00:45:06,670
我对我弟弟绝无二心
I am loyal to my brother,

691
00:45:06,740 --> 00:45:10,640
但我为将来担心  非常担心
but I fear the future. I fear it.

692
00:45:10,710 --> 00:45:15,310
我问自己  若是国王忙得无暇理会我们
And I ask myself, what do we mean to the king

693
00:45:15,380 --> 00:45:17,950
那我们对他来说究竟算什么
if he's too busy for us?

694
00:45:40,740 --> 00:45:43,140
总算来了啊
Finally!

695
00:45:56,920 --> 00:46:00,860
别傻站着  帮忙啊
Well, don't just stand there! Help me!

696
00:46:00,930 --> 00:46:03,200
我说过科尔弗将被驱逐出这里
You were told Colfur was to be banished!

697
00:46:03,260 --> 00:46:06,030
你以为你的话在这还能管用
You think your words mean anything here,

698
